0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ArianaGrande-reflects-on-album-success-Eternal-Sunshine-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ArianaGrande-reflects-on-album-success-Eternal-Sunshine-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ArianaGrande-reflects-on-album-success-Eternal-Sunshine-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ArianaGrande-reflects-on-album-success-Eternal-Sunshine-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ArianaGrande-reflects-on-album-success-Eternal-Sunshine-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a>回顾了她的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ariana-grande-eternal-sunshine-lyrics-tracklist-3598038">《永恒的阳光》(Eternal Sunshine)</a>受到的“压倒性的爱的反应”。</p><p>该唱片于本月早些时候（3 月 8 日）发行，是这位歌手继 2020 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ariana-grande-positions-album-review-2805145">《Positions》</a>之后的第七个完整项目。其中包括单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ariana-grande-new-single-yes-and-lyrics-video-review-3569651">“Yes, And?”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ariana-grande-perform-two-new-eternal-sunshine-songs-on-snl-3599228">“我们不能成为朋友（等待你的爱）”</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ariana-grande-eternal-sunshine-lyrics-tracklist-3598038">爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande) – 《永恒的阳光》评论：一篇引人注目的情绪作品</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Eternal Sunshine》为 Grande 赢得了她在美国<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/ariana-grande-we-cant-be-friends-global-charts-number-one-debut-1235635815/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard 200</em></a>排行榜上的第六张专辑，以及在英国的第五张专辑（通过<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/ariana-grande-eternal-sunshine-fifth-number-1-album/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜</em></a>）。</p><p>这位流行歌星昨晚（3 月 18 日）在 Instagram 上写信给粉丝，她在回顾这张唱片的成功和反响时表示，她“只是想从心底感谢你们”。</p><p> “无法用语言来形容我这周的感受。这张专辑对我来说是最特别的，原因有很多，而且包含了很多东西，”格兰德继续说道。</p><p> “分享它重新开启了很多大大小小的感受，从很多方面来说，这都是激动人心的一周！……但你对这一切的强烈爱的回应让我感到如此快乐、人与人之间的联系和安慰。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4quNIBuwxP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 55